== Access == * '''Ōji-ga-ue Park:''' About 850m northeast from [[:en:Sakaihigashi Station|Sakaihigashi Station]] on the [[:en:Koya Line|Nankai Kōya Line]], operated by [[:en:Nankai Electric Railway|Nankai Electric Railway]]. ** From Sakaihigashi Station, head north along the railway towards Namba, and turn east after the third railway crossing. * '''{{ill|Sugawara Shrine (Sakai)|ja|菅原神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugawara Shrine (Sakai)|qq=}}:''' About 300m southeast from {{ill|Hanataguchi Station|ja|花田口停留場|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hanataguchi Station|qq=}} on the [[:en:Hankai Line|Hankai Line]], operated by [[:en:Hankai Tramway|Hankai Tramway]].
